-Oh, she might have
a point with that.

17:57.080 --> 17:59.000
Could be.

17:59.040 --> 18:00.720
Don't come here with
your bloody sensible,
rational views.

18:02.920 --> 18:05.160
No, actually it's funny
you should mention
the Middle Eastern market,

18:05.200 --> 18:07.920
because they've also done one
for fly-fishing,
which happens in the Yemen.

18:07.960 --> 18:09.400
-Yeah.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.480
-JAMES: It does.

18:13.400 --> 18:14.680
JEREMY: And it gets better.

18:15.840 --> 18:17.360
And falconry.

18:17.400 --> 18:19.600
And falconry's really big
in the Middle East.

18:19.640 --> 18:21.200
What about dogging?

18:23.520 --> 18:26.320
-Well, why don't they do one
for dogging?

18:26.360 --> 18:31.040
It's a countryside pursuit,
and more people do that
than do falconry, don't they?

18:31.080 --> 18:34.080
-Well, yeah, you're prob...
probably right.
-Yeah.

18:34.120 --> 18:36.080
-From what I've heard.
-RICHARD: Well, they should.

18:36.120 --> 18:39.200
-But what would you have
in a dogging Bentayga, then?

18:39.240 --> 18:40.880
Well, you'd open the drawers
and there'd be like--

18:40.920 --> 18:42.800
-MAN: Wet wipes.
